WEBVTT

00:23.048 --> 00:24.732
The magic Luz's abuela did...

00:24.809 --> 00:26.642
I spoke to Jirou.

00:26.719 --> 00:28.218
I touched him.
He was real.

00:28.296 --> 00:29.904
Give her the baby in this
picture?

00:29.981 --> 00:33.132
The magic only works if the
person in the image is dead.

00:47.857 --> 00:49.715
Oh. Oh, God.

03:17.122 --> 03:19.390
Is it Fourth of July?

03:21.293 --> 03:23.644
No, it's August.

03:23.646 --> 03:24.645
I go look.

03:24.647 --> 03:25.479
No, don't go out alone.

03:25.481 --> 03:26.939
Wait!
Oh...

03:28.467 --> 03:29.467
Yamato-san...

03:31.879 --> 03:34.071
Yamato-san, slow down.

03:48.338 --> 03:50.654
Hey! Hey, son!

03:50.656 --> 03:52.006
Sonny!

03:52.008 --> 03:53.490
What's going on?

03:53.492 --> 03:54.324
We did it!

03:54.326 --> 03:55.176
What?

03:55.178 --> 03:56.178
We got 'em!

03:57.013 --> 03:58.662
We bombed the Japs!

03:58.664 --> 03:59.697
Whoo!

03:59.699 --> 04:01.891
We hit Hiroshima!

04:08.191 --> 04:10.416
They'll have to surrender!

04:49.943 --> 04:54.943
